query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('axapta',
'compact-framework',
'endianness',
'excel-2010',
'grammar',
'materialize',
'obfuscation',
'redhat',
'scenekit',
'system.reactive',
'x509certificate');
